In [65]:
def objective_fn(trial,trainX,trainY):
    hiddenNos = trial.suggest_int('hiddenNos',10,80,log=True)
    hiddenNos2 = trial.suggest_int('hiddenNos2',10,30,log=True)
    lr = trial.suggest_categorical('lr',['constant','invscaling'])
    activation = trial.suggest_categorical('activation',['logistic','relu','tanh'])
    clf = MLPClassifier(hidden_layer_sizes=(hiddenNos,hiddenNos2),activation=activation,learning_rate=lr,random_state=100,max_iter=3000)

    res = model_selection.cross_val_score(clf,trainX.values,trainY.values,scoring='accuracy',cv=5,n_jobs=-1)

    return res.mean()
In [66]:

    • Principal component analysis, PCA
